the LORD God of Israel. Reference to Pentateuch (Exodus 32:27 . CompareJoshua 9:18, Joshua 9:19; Joshua 10:40, Joshua 10:42 , &c). See note onIsaiah 29:23 .

God of Israel. Reference to Pentateuch (Exodus 24:10. Numbers 16:9). Occurs in latter part of Isaiah (Isaiah 41:17 ;Isaiah 45:3 ;Isaiah 48:2).
